# Methodology

## 1. Protein Preparation
- Protein (7SFB) downloaded from RCSB PDB
- Water molecules removed
- Hydrogens added using PyMOL

## 2. Ligand Preparation
- Ligands downloaded from PubChem
- Converted to the appropriate format using Open Babel

## 3. Drug-Likeness
- Evaluated using SwissADME
- Lipinski Rule of Five applied

## 4. ADMET Prediction
- Performed using ADMETlab

## 5. Binding Site Prediction
- Active site identified using CASTp / PrankWeb

## 6. Molecular Docking
- Docking performed using PyRx / AutoDock
- Binding energies recorded and analyzed

## 7. Visualization
- Interactions visualized using PyMOL
